						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up near the eastern entrance into the Kalamēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription, dated in <hi rend="bold">Chaitra ba. Ashṭami, Bhāskaravāra</hi> (Sunday), records the death of <hi rend="bold">Māchiga,</hi> son of a certain <hi rend="bold">Kēta.</hi> The characters belong to about the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
