<p>
<lb n="1"/>© dhāriṇigādi caitra bahuḷāṣṭami bhāskaravāra
<lb n="2" break="no"/>doḷu mahādhīranenippa mācigana vīratana
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kkati mecci bhairavaṁ bārene kūḍikoṁḍanenu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tōrvvananurvvare ba(ṁ)ṇnisalu savistārade
<lb n="5"/>kētanātmasutaneydidaneydidanūr<unclear>dhva</unclear>lōkava
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nu <g type="ddanda">.</g> vu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> dippayvatirvvaru neṟevī
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ranaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> bana sahitaṁturvviyo
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> varagurvva <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> yvatta mūva
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rjjagadoḷu <g type="ddanda">.</g> maṁgaḷa mahāśrī <g type="ddanda">.</g> 
